Permissions on Course pages:
=========================

On Grappelli:
---------------------

> cd /etc/apache2/sites-enabled/
> gvim www.life

	Go the section for the course that needs change in permissions or needs a new user to be added. Make the changes (add/delete user/group)

If not here see in :
> gvim /etc/group


Restart apache:
> apache2ctl graceful


Scenario:
Why can't I download the pdfs on this course page? 
http://www.life.illinois.edu/ib/452/readings.html
http://www.life.illinois.edu/mcb/426/

Ans: It's because they have no permission to download. It needs to be added.

